OL,3,CSouthport riots report: Police 'ill-
OL,4,Cequipped' to tackle impact of online
OL,5,Ccontent
OL,7,FThe UK's police watchdog has warned
OL,8,Fthat forces are "ill-equipped" to deal
OL,9,Fwith the risks of online content, in a
OL,10,Freport commissioned in the wake of
OL,11,Flast year's summer riots.
OL,13,FProtests in Southport escalated into
OL,14,Fwidespread disorder across England
OL,15,Fafter three young girls, Bebe King,
OL,16,FElsie Dot Stancombe and Alice Da Silva
OL,17,FAguiar, were murdered at a Taylor
OL,18,FSwift-themed dance class last July.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
