OL,3,CSouthport riots report: Police 'ill-
OL,4,Cequipped' to tackle impact of online
OL,5,Ccontent
OL,7,FThe report, by His Majesty's
OL,8,FInspectorate of Constabulary and Fire
OL,9,F& Rescue Services (HMICFRS), found
OL,10,Fpolice forces simply could not keep up
OL,11,Fwith the speed of false narratives
OL,12,Fbeing spread online - particularly in
OL,13,Frelation to the girls' killer, Axel
OL,14,FRudakubana, who has since been
OL,15,Fsentenced to 52 years in prison.
OL,17,FAnd they did not do enough to counter
OL,18,Fthem, HMICFRS said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
