OL,3,CSouthport riots report: Police 'ill-
OL,4,Cequipped' to tackle impact of online
OL,5,Ccontent
OL,7,FHis Majesty's Chief Inspector of
OL,8,FConstabulary Sir Andy Cooke said
OL,9,Fmisinformation and disinformation
OL,10,Fposted on social media helped "fan the
OL,11,Fflames of disorder" last summer, and
OL,12,Fmisleading posts were left up too long.
OL,14,F"Sadly, when these massive issues
OL,15,Fhappen, like the despicable murders of
OL,16,Fthree young girls in Southport, there
OL,17,Fis a real craving for information from
OL,18,Fthe public", Sir Andy told ITV News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
