OL,3,CSouthport riots report: Police 'ill-
OL,4,Cequipped' to tackle impact of online
OL,5,Ccontent
OL,7,F"If the police don't fill that void,
OL,8,Fother people will - and it's quite
OL,9,Foften filled with untruths, lies,
OL,10,Fmisinformation or gossip."
OL,12,F'If police don't fill the information
OL,13,Fvoid, other people will', says His
OL,14,FMajesty's Chief Inspector of
OL,15,FConstabulary Sir Andy Cooke
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
