OL,3,CSouthport riots report: Police 'ill-
OL,4,Cequipped' to tackle impact of online
OL,5,Ccontent
OL,7,FHe said there was a disparity across
OL,8,Fforces in how equipped they are to
OL,9,Fdeal with these issues. For example,
OL,10,Fthe Metropolitan Police has a
OL,11,Fdedicated team to investigate major
OL,12,Fdisorder.
OL,14,FSir Andy said: "Some forces are still
OL,15,Fnot prepared to deal with this
OL,16,Fmisinformation (or) disinformation
OL,17,Fwhen it comes out.
