OL,3,CSouthport riots report: Police 'ill-
OL,4,Cequipped' to tackle impact of online
OL,5,Ccontent
OL,7,F"They need to focus on this because
OL,8,Fit's not going to go away, it's going
OL,9,Fto get worse and worse and more
OL,10,Fdifficult for forces to deal with."
OL,12,FHe also pointed to social media
OL,13,Fcompanies "social responsibility" to
OL,14,Ftake down harmful content on their
OL,15,Fplatforms and separate freedom of
OL,16,Fspeech from "outright lies" and
OL,17,Fincitement to violence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
