OL,3,CSouthport riots report: Police 'ill-
OL,4,Cequipped' to tackle impact of online
OL,5,Ccontent
OL,7,F"They have a responsibility to quickly
OL,8,Ftake down these posts when they have
OL,9,Fthe evidence to support the fact that
OL,10,Fwhat is being proposed that is not the
OL,11,Ftruth," he added.
OL,13,FThe HMICFRS report also highlighted
OL,14,Fnational assessments that said the
OL,15,Frisk of unrest was low, despite
OL,16,Fvolatility in society at the time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
