OL,3,CSouthport riots report: Police 'ill-
OL,4,Cequipped' to tackle impact of online
OL,5,Ccontent
OL,7,FIt said the lack of a police
OL,8,Fintelligence network dealing
OL,9,Fspecifically with disorder is a
OL,10,Fproblem, and called for a return to
OL,11,Fneighbourhood policing so that
OL,12,Fofficers are more aware of tensions
OL,13,Fthat may be simmering in their area.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
