OL,3,CSouthport riots report: Police 'ill-
OL,4,Cequipped' to tackle impact of online
OL,5,Ccontent
OL,7,FOn whether greater intelligence
OL,8,Fsharing could have completely
OL,9,Fprevented the riots, Sir Andy said: "I
OL,10,Fthink whilst it's difficult to say
OL,11,Fwhether it could have been totally
OL,12,Fprevented, I think we would have seen
OL,13,Fless disorder if policing would have
OL,14,Fbeen in a different place - to
OL,15,Factually mobilise more quickly, to
OL,16,Fhave the right people in the right
OL,17,Fplace at the right times.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
