OL,3,CSouthport riots report: Police 'ill-
OL,4,Cequipped' to tackle impact of online
OL,5,Ccontent
OL,7,F"But you can't do that if you don't
OL,8,Fbuild your intelligence before these
OL,9,Fissues happen, and good intelligence
OL,10,Fis the best way to prevent an awful
OL,11,Flot of the violence that did occur."
